{"tid":1318681,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"土瓜灣遊行的朋友要留心","createTime":"2019-07-15T03:52:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T21:56:59.000Z","uid":112205,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"554a305509167283d324562bfed74e3dde553e43","tid":1318681,"uid":112205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:52:45.000Z","msg":"土瓜灣依個地方，係藍絲、新移民及廢老的集中地<br />\n<br />\n依個地方，雖然交通方便，但道路被block曬的話就冇車走到<br />\n一方面，條廢鐵沙中線未開; 另一方面，土瓜灣地勢平原，冇任何天橋、冇商場。<br />\n所以大家走的時候要留心<br />\n最近的地鐵站係何文田，要行好遠路<br />\n<br />\n土瓜灣分上下部份，近海心公園一帶就係下路，係旅遊巴、劏蝗客的集中地<br />\n上路就係樂民新村、民居集中地<br />\n<br />\n要去遊行的朋友，記得好好安排路線!"},{"pid":"eab723abba6894a090bb7757e562a3b2940aaa9a","tid":1318681,"uid":47272,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:05:20.000Z","msg":"啟德隧道口有行人天橋"},{"pid":"463bd99ba741fe24190e0bb189784e27d2b0bdd8","tid":1318681,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:06:46.000Z","msg":"最低成本既方法，又減低傷亡，和理非都可以幫手<br />\n請幫手推！！<br />\n<br />\n警告你地唔好再屌警察老母<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1317630\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1317630</a>"},{"pid":"044d1ad162ab95ae5c78c9bfede2e8e67f7611be","tid":1318681,"uid":79252,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:06:58.000Z","msg":"其實係咪應該調返轉嚟行"},{"pid":"5db46013f4c8268b0c27c274ede93027f89f9fd8","tid":1318681,"uid":79252,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"044d1ad162ab95ae5c78c9bfede2e8e67f7611be","tid":1318681,"uid":79252,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:06:58.000Z","msg":"其實係咪應該調返轉嚟行"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:07:46.000Z","msg":"九龍城個位根本走唔到"},{"pid":"da8d84b8be25faa317878618dd15b243888d16d1","tid":1318681,"uid":256281,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:18:52.000Z","msg":"有咩事走上何文田 入山避"},{"pid":"31ec778685674e3072b8c878453f25c4de6909b9","tid":1318681,"uid":74908,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"da8d84b8be25faa317878618dd